Invocation Name: barky bark
des:
Noisy barking dogs - who doesn't enjoy that? Just open the skill to get the party started. Devices with a screen get a random photo.

The dogs used are West Highland terriers. No animals were harmed in the making of this skill but some humans were driven a little crazy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
